title: 149 6 "Steer for the Clouds! Capture the South Bird!"Transliteration: "Kumo kaji ippai! Sausubādo o oe!" (Japanese:雲舵いっぱい!サウスバードを追え!) Yuji Endo Yoshiyuki Suga March 23, 2003(2003-03-23)[15] November 3, 2007[16][17]
transformers_text: 149 6 Steer for the Clouds Capture the South Bird Transliteration Kum o kaj i ip pai Sau sub do o oe Japanese Yuji Endo Yoshiyuki Suga March 23 2003 2003 03 23 15 November 3 2007 16 17 Cricket explains how the Straw Hats can ride a dangerous vertical current called the Knock Up Stream to get to Sky pie a However they first have to catch a south bird to point them toward the point where the stream will erupt from the ocean
